z.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-deputy-mayor-posts-photos-with-blindfolded-shackled-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-9c15-d6da-a1cf-ff379d6b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于供应短缺和以色列袭击造成的不安全局势，联合国停止在拉法分发粮食</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/un-halts-food-distribution-in-rafah-due-to-supply-shortages-insecurity-from-idf-strikes/0000018f-9c9a-da3b-a7ff-9f9fb1f60000</link><description>联合国表示，加沙约有 110 万人（近一半人口）面临灾难性的饥饿，该地区正处于饥荒的边缘。自5月6日以色列入侵拉法以来，人道主义物资危机在两周内加剧</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/un-halts-food-distribution-in-rafah-due-to-supply-shortages-insecurity-from-idf-strikes/0000018f-9c9a-da3b-a7ff-9f9fb1f60000</guid></item><item><title>“让战争机器挨饿”：加州大学圣克鲁斯分校的工人罢工声援亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/workers-at-uc-santa-cruz-go-on-strike-in-solidarity-with-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-9bf8-da35-a3af-dffa0a620000</link><description>周一，数百名罢工工人在加州大学学校集会，重点关注该州加沙营地的“警察镇压”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/workers-at-uc-santa-cruz-go-on-strike-in-solidarity-with-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-9bf8-da35-a3af-dffa0a620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡已经彻底迷失方向了吗？或许。但也许是故意的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/has-netanyahu-completely-lost-his-bearings-maybe-but-maybe-its-intentional/0000018f-9bb6-da35-a3af-dfbeacb70000</link><description>人们很容易说，以色列是由一个在严重的政治胁迫下绝望的人领导的，他似乎患有相互交织的综合症，这些综合症曾困扰着他之前的路易十四和沙贝泰·兹维等人。好吧，如果它真的被领导的话</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 18:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/has-netanyahu-completely-lost-his-bearings-maybe-but-maybe-its-intentional/0000018f-9bb6-da35-a3af-dfbeacb70000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷，而不是海牙：以色列必须调查内塔尼亚胡在加沙犯下的危害人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-not-the-hague-israel-must-investigate-netanyahu-for-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-9bee-d6da-a1cf-fbeeec0d0000</link><description>回应国际刑事法院逮捕令请求的唯一有效方法是召集以色列国家调查委员会，调查加沙人民是否被故意挨饿——而不是大喊反犹太主义和纳粹主义</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 17:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-not-the-hague-israel-must-investigate-netanyahu-for-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-9bee-d6da-a1cf-fbeeec0d0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 228 天：本-格维尔表示，以色列应该在战后控制加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-228-israel-should-control-gaza-after-the-war-ben-gvir-says/0000018f-9bfc-d264-a1bf-dfffe0c20000</link><description>以色列敦促“文明世界国家”反对国际刑事法院检察官的要求 ■ 国家安全顾问表示，美国即将与沙特阿拉伯达成升级关系的历史性协议 ■ 本-格维尔：以色列应该在战后控制加沙 ■ 以色列官员夺取广播以色列南部属于美联社的设备 ■ 以色列国防军称其在杰宁发起了反恐行动 ■ 战争进入 228 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-228-israel-should-control-gaza-after-the-war-ben-gvir-says/0000018f-9bfc-d264-a1bf-dfffe0c20000</guid></item><item><title>猛烈抨击国际刑事法院，以色列“官方”反对派与内塔尼亚胡腐败一样懦弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-21/ty-article/.highlight/slamming-icc-israels-official-opposition-is-as-craven-as-netanyahu-is-corrupt/0000018f-9bde-da35-a3af-dffe8eea0000</link><description>包括反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德在内的绝大多数以色列议员在一封谴责国际刑事法院检察官汗预审令的信上签名。以色列议会中只有少数人明白，内塔尼亚胡是否“和辛瓦尔一样糟糕”，或者反之亦然，都无关紧要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-21/ty-article/.highlight/slamming-icc-israels-official-opposition-is-as-craven-as-netanyahu-is-corrupt/0000018f-9bde-da35-a3af-dffe8eea0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡警告国际刑事法院的汗：我不担心出国，“他应该担心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-warns-iccs-khan-im-not-concerned-over-going-abroad-he-should-be-worried/0000018f-9b5e-dce9-a1cf-ffde9c400000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡驳回了国际刑事法院针对他和国防部长加兰特的逮捕令申请，称其为“热门工作”，并将其与 9 月 11 日后对乔治·布什或二战后对富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福发出逮捕令进行比较</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-warns-iccs-khan-im-not-concerned-over-going-abroad-he-should-be-worried/0000018f-9b5e-dce9-a1cf-ffde9c400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家档案馆丢失了也门儿童失踪事件的文件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-lose-documents-on-missing-yemenite-children-affair/0000018f-9ae3-da35-a3af-dfeb52a60000</link><description>根据州审计长的报告，一台装有这些文件的电脑被借给了一名员工，但此后就失踪了。报告还发现，138份文件被借给员工且从未归还，并且由于不当行为，信息并未向公众提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-lose-documents-on-missing-yemenite-children-affair/0000018f-9ae3-da35-a3af-dfeb52a60000</guid></item><item><title>阿鲁夫·本：“以色列有办法对抗美国并逃脱惩罚”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-21/ty-article-podcast/aluf-benn-israel-has-a-way-of-standing-up-to-the-u-s-and-getting-away-with-it/0000018f-9b0f-dce9-a1cf-ffcf7f2d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-21/ty-article-podcast/aluf-benn-israel-has-a-way-of-standing-up-to-the-u-s-and-getting-away-with-it/0000018f-9b0f-dce9-a1cf-ffcf7f2d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列驻瑞典大使在持续威胁下保持乐观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ambassador-to-sweden-remains-optimistic-while-working-under-constant-threats/0000018f-9a6c-dce9-a1cf-feecb91f0000</link><description>齐夫·内沃·库尔曼 (Ziv Nevo Kulman) 于 2021 年上任，当时正值以色列-瑞典关系史上最困难的危机之一。 10 月 7 日，其他声音也浮出水面。他在接受《国土报》采访时表示，“突然间，我们发现在核心问题上达成了共识”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ambassador-to-sweden-remains-optimistic-while-working-under-constant-threats/0000018f-9a6c-dce9-a1cf-feecb91f0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国施压下，以色列通讯部长表示当局将归还美联社扣押的设备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/israeli-officials-seize-ap-equipment-halt-gaza-live-broadcast-citing-al-jazeera-law/0000018f-9b4e-dce9-a1cf-ffce461c0000</link><description>以色列官员周二早些时候抵达以色列南部的美联社地点，没收了他们的设备，声称他们向半岛电视台提供加沙的图像，违反了该国新的外国广播法</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/israeli-officials-seize-ap-equipment-halt-gaza-live-broadcast-citing-al-jazeera-law/0000018f-9b4e-dce9-a1cf-ffce461c0000</guid></item><item><title>校园抗议以色列的良性反犹太主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-virtuous-antisemitism-of-campus-protests-against-israel/0000018f-9aa0-d264-a1bf-deb7652f0000</link><description>示威者可以剥夺以色列人的生存权，因为在他们眼中，他们正在捍卫一个受到暴徒国家威胁的世界</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:32:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-virtuous-antisemitism-of-campus-protests-against-israel/0000018f-9aa0-d264-a1bf-deb7652f0000</guid></item><item><title>“姐妹，请原谅我们：”亲巴勒斯坦批评者对阿迈勒·克鲁尼对以色列加沙战争保持沉默感到遗憾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-critics-regret-bashing-amal-clooney-for-silence-on-israel-war-in-gaza/0000018f-9ab5-dce9-a1cf-fef5ad2f0000</link><description>推特批评者此前曾痛斥国际人权律师阿迈勒·克鲁尼没有就加沙局势发表任何公开声明，但当她加入国际刑事法院小组审查加沙战争罪行的消息曝光后，他们道歉并赞扬她</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 11:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-critics-regret-bashing-amal-clooney-for-silence-on-israel-war-in-gaza/0000018f-9ab5-dce9-a1cf-fef5ad2f0000</guid></item><item><title>医生恳求世卫组织利用影响力保障加沙人质的福祉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/doctors-implore-who-to-use-leverage-for-well-being-of-hostages-in-gaza/0000018f-9a87-d6da-a1cf-fba7506a0000</link><description>该请愿书由两名以色列医生发起，他们呼吁世界卫生组织立即采取行动，确保人质的健康，目前全球已有 1000 多名医生签署了该请愿书。一名医生痛惜道：“有一种感觉，世界正在忘记人质”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/doctors-implore-who-to-use-leverage-for-well-being-of-hostages-in-gaza/0000018f-9a87-d6da-a1cf-fba7506a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸杰宁，七名巴勒斯坦人丧生，其中包括骑自行车的青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-raid-in-west-bank-city-of-jenin/0000018f-9a9a-d6da-a1cf-fbba1e850000</link><description>以色列军方表示，已在杰宁启动反恐行动，并已确认至少15名受伤武装分子的身份。伊斯兰圣战组织宣布其特工正在参加战斗</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:18:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-raid-in-west-bank-city-of-jenin/0000018f-9a9a-d6da-a1cf-fbba1e850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长表示，加沙的军事统治将把以色列国防军的义务兵役期延长至四年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-defense-minister-says-military-rule-in-gaza-would-extend-idf-service-to-4-years/0000018f-9a58-d6da-a1cf-fb7ae2ac0000</link><description>国防部长约阿夫·加兰特告诉利库德集团议员，以色列对加沙的军事统治将使军队付出沉重代价，并呼吁建立替代政府。他的同事批评他，称他试图将加沙交给巴勒斯坦权力机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-defense-minister-says-military-rule-in-gaza-would-extend-idf-service-to-4-years/0000018f-9a58-d6da-a1cf-fb7ae2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问：沙特协议已完成；美国可能向以色列展示草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-saudi-deal-close-u-s-may-show-draft-to-israel/0000018f-9a0d-d35f-a1df-dfcd52110000</link><description>沙利文向以色列高级官员澄清，在升级沙特阿拉伯关系的协议方面已经取得进展，但表示担心内塔尼亚胡在巴勒斯坦问题上的立场会破坏谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-saudi-deal-close-u-s-may-show-draft-to-israel/0000018f-9a0d-d35f-a1df-dfcd52110000</guid></item></channel></rss>